171 A.3d 1257 DIANNA QUAMINA, PLAINTIFF-PETITIONER, v. STELLA GARDENS APARTMENTS, DEFENDANT-RESPONDENT.

C-212 Sept.Term 2017

079309 October 20, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002910-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

*101It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
